_sText:
This map was made for gmod, I just converted it for use in css as a FY_ map.  

It's set at an ancient river that runs through temple ruins and tiki docks.  You can enter the temple to encounter traps, if you can get past them you get the treasure.  There's also a huge volcano looming in the distance.

The screenshots were not modified at all, that's how it really looks in game.  Just make sure you have color correction enabled in options and you're running a DX9 card.
